---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Premium Template | Jobcoach Website" description="Premium Design für Jobcoaches – exklusiv, luxuriös, erstklassig.">
  <div class="demo-page">
    <header class="demo-header">
      <div class="demo-badge">Premium Template</div>
      <a href="/order?template=premium" class="btn-use">Dieses Template wählen →</a>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero premium-hero">
      <div class="hero-bg"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="logo-monogram">AF</div>
        <div class="badge-premium">★ Premium</div>
        <h1>Alexander Falk</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Senior Executive Coach · Frankfurt<br/>Für Leaders, die mehr wollen</p>
        
        <div class="credentials">
          <span class="credential-badge">EMCC EIA</span>
          <span class="credential-badge">ProCert</span>
          <span class="credential-badge">20+ Jahre</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Value Prop -->
    <section class="value-prop">
      <div class="value-grid">
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-num">€200K+</div>
          <div class="value-label">Durchschnittl. Gehaltsplus meiner Klienten</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-num">94%</div>
          <div class="value-label">Erfolgsquote bei Führungskräfte-Coaching</div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-num">3 Monate</div>
          <div class="value-label">Ø bis zur Beförderung oder Jobwechsel</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="about">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Executive Background,<br/>Coach-Expertise</h2>
        <p>20 Jahre in globalen Konzernen (Siemens, BMW, McKinsey-Alumni) haben mir gezeigt, was wirklich funktioniert – und was nicht.</p>
        <p>Heute coache ich C-Suite Executives und High Potentials, die den nächsten Karriereschritt machen wollen: Vorstandspositionen, Aufsichtsräte, Founding Roles.</p>
        <div class="certifications">
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="cert-label">Mitgliedschaften</span>
            <span>EMCC · ICF · DBVC</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="cert-label">Zertifizierungen</span>
            <span>Master Coach (ECA) · Systemic Constellation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cert-item">
            <span class="cert-label">Ausbildung</span>
            <span>MBA INSEAD · Psychologie (Uni Köln)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section class="services">
      <h2>Exclusive Leistungen</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card premium-card">
          <div class="service-tier">I</div>
          <h3>Executive Intensive</h3>
          <p>3-monatiges 1:1 Programm für Vorstandsmitglieder und C-Level. Wöchentliche Sessions + Notfall-Support.</p>
          <div class="price">ab €8.500<span>/Quartal</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">II</div>
          <h3>Career Acceleration</h3>
          <p>6-wöchiges Programm für High Potentials. Ziel: Beförderung oder strategischer Jobwechsel.</p>
          <div class="price">ab €3.800<span>/Programm</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">III</div>
          <h3>Board Advisory</h3>
          <p>Langfristige Begleitung für Aufsichtsratsmandate und Supervisory Boards. Quarterly Meetings.</p>
          <div class="price">ab €12.000<span>/Jahr</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>Ergebnisse zählen</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-list">
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">"Alexander hat meine Verhandlungsstrategie für den Vorstandsposten revolutioniert. 40% Gehaltserhöhung inklusive."</div>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">— CEO eines DAX-30 Unternehmens</div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">"In 4 Monaten vom Abteilungsleiter zum Geschäftsführer – Alexanders Coaching war der Schlüssel."</div>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">— Managing Director, Consulting</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="contact-cta">
      <h2>First Meeting on Invitation Only</h2>
      <p>Ich nehme nur 12 Klienten pro Jahr an. Wenn du bereit bist für den nächsten Level, lass uns sprechen.</p>
      <a href="/order?template=premium" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
        Kontakt aufnehmen ★
      </a>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>© 2026 Alexander Falk Executive Coaching · Frankfurt</p>
      <p class="legal-links">
        <a href="/impressum">Impressum</a> · <a href="/datenschutz">Datenschutz</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: #030712;
    color: #f1f5f9;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>

<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #d4af37;
    --gold-light: #f4d58d;
    --gold-dark: #aa8c2c;
    --bg-dark: #030712;
    --bg-card: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05);
    --text: #f1f5f9;
    --text-muted: #9ca3af;
  }

  .demo-page { min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

  .demo-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.95);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
  }

  .demo-badge {
    background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .btn-use {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-dark));
    color: #030712;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-use:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .logo-monogram {
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
  }

  .badge-premium {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-dark));
    color: #030712;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .credentials {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .credential-badge {
    background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Value Prop */
  .value-prop {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.03);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .value-item { text-align: center; }

  .value-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .value-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 150px;
  }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content { text-align: center; }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .about p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .certifications {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .cert-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05);
  }

  .cert-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .cert-item span:last-child {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Services */
  .services {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services h2 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-card.premium-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08), rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.02));
    border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .service-tier {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .price span { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; }

  /* Testimonials */
  .testimonials {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
  }

  .testimonials h2 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .testimonials-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .testimonial-meta {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .contact-cta {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .contact-cta p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-dark));
    color: #030712;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-large { padding: 18px 36px; font-size: 1rem; }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  }

  .legal-links { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .legal-links a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .cert-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
  }
</style>